Subject: Re: [VB] RGB oil level

I think the amount of oil for the RGB's is 8 oz. The RGB's in my bus seem to
have a connection to the tranee. Oil will flow thru the axel tubes and I
assume it goes both ways. So If you did the initial fill on the RGB's and
your tranee is full, All should be OK.

Chris

